findings.title: Unused Functions
findings.description: Consider removing unused functions to save gas and improve codebase readability and cleanliness.

findings.title: Owner can mint after initial deployment
findings.description: The owner of the contract has the ability to mint new tokens even after the initial deployment.

findings.title: Owner can update total fees with an indefinite amount
findings.description: The owner of the contract has the ability to update total fees without any limitations, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can pause trading
findings.description: The owner of the contract has the ability to pause trading.
